    "Our model addresses this challenge by simulating artificial communities with arbitrary levels of rhetorical citing.",
    "This enables us to turn rhetorical citing on and off and measure its effects.",
    "Second, even if such communities did exist, classifying citations as substantive or rhetorical is difficult.",
    "For classification, one approach uses machine learning with training data from third-party labelers 26,27, but how well such labels correspond to authors' actual motivations is unclear.",
